{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 All automation, even from tracks without any items, will be copied.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 NOTE: A potential problem is that pre-existing envelope points in the area where the automation is pasted will not be overwritten, so old and new points will be mixed.\par}
