{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Provides a variety of options for creating time selections at the edit cursor, and can export specific settings as a separate action.\par}
